summary.purpose: Provides green and gray crane SVG icon generator functions conforming to the VehicleSvg signature for use as map markers and menu icons.
summary.problem_solved: Supplies the crane vehicle type's green (moving) and gray (unknown) icon variants. Red and yellow crane variants are in cranes1.tsx.

exports.name: greenCraneIcon
exports.description_one_line: Returns a green crane SVG element with configurable size, site colour, CSS class, and viewBox context.

exports.name: grayCraneIcon
exports.description_one_line: Returns a gray crane SVG element with configurable size, site colour, CSS class, and viewBox context.

symbols.name: greenCraneIcon
symbols.description_one_line: Returns a green crane SVG element with configurable size, site colour, CSS class, and viewBox context.

params.name: width
params.description: Width attribute for the SVG element.

params.name: height
params.description: Height attribute for the SVG element.

params.name: siteColor
params.description: Fill colour for site-specific colour accents.

params.name: className
params.description: CSS class name applied to the SVG element.

returns.description: Green crane icon SVG element. Green indicates the crane is actively moving.

details.what_it_does: Generates a detailed crane SVG icon in green, indicating the crane vehicle is actively moving (speed > 0).

minimal_correct.title: Render a green crane icon
minimal_correct.code:
import { greenCraneIcon } from 'akeyless-assets-commons';

const icon = greenCraneIcon('30', '30', '#00FF00', 'newIconCar', 'map_icon');

symbols.name: grayCraneIcon
symbols.description_one_line: Returns a gray crane SVG element with configurable size, site colour, CSS class, and viewBox context.

params.name: width
params.description: Width attribute for the SVG element.

params.name: height
params.description: Height attribute for the SVG element.

params.name: siteColor
params.description: Fill colour for site-specific colour accents.

params.name: className
params.description: CSS class name applied to the SVG element.

returns.description: Gray crane icon SVG element. Gray indicates unknown telemetry state.

details.what_it_does: Generates a detailed crane SVG icon in gray, indicating telemetry data is unavailable for the crane vehicle.

minimal_correct.title: Render a gray crane icon
minimal_correct.code:
import { grayCraneIcon } from 'akeyless-assets-commons';

const icon = grayCraneIcon('30', '30', '#888888', 'newIconCar', 'map_icon');
